source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_SEQ_00<tab>Fibubb Gah wishes to salvage the honor taken from his people.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_SEQ_00<tab>Fibubb Gah semble révolté par quelque chose.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_SEQ_01<tab>Fibubb Gah, unable to overlook the common thievery of the fallen Amalj'aa, wishes you to reclaim the ancestral weapons of the Forgotten Springs Miqo'te. Recover the unearned spoils of war from the crude gold coffers found in Zanr'ak, and also from the cooling corpses of an Amalj'aa brigand and an Amalj'aa scavenger.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_SEQ_01<tab>Fibubb Gah vous explique que les Amalj'aa de Zahar'ak ont dérobé aux Miqo'tes leurs accessoires de chasse traditionnels, et qu'il a décidé de les leur restituer. Il vous demande d'aller à l'ouest du camp de Zahar'ak et de fouiller les <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E90C00302 /var> pour y trouver des pièges, un arc et une lance de chasse miqo'tes.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_SEQ_02<tab>You have retrieved the Miqo'te weapons. Deliver the assorted arms to Fibubb Gah at the Ring of Ash.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez récupéré les accessoires de chasse des Miqo'tes. Apportez-les à présent à Fibubb Gah.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_SEQ_03<tab>Though he claims no ties of fellowship with the U tribe, Fibubb Gah nevertheless feels honor-bound to return the unfairly won weaponry to Forgotten Springs himself. The Brotherhood soldier praises your well-rounded warrior spirit, and is certain that your feet are firmly planted on the path to greatness.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_SEQ_03<tab>Vous avez remis les objets à Fibubb Gah, qui s'est engagé à les restituer. Fibubb Gah semble avoir encore plus de respect pour vous en tant que guerrier, et il croit plus que jamais en votre sens de l'honneur. Continuez à lui venir en aide lorsqu'il vous le demandera.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_TODO_00<tab>Obtain caches of ranger weapons from crude gold coffers in Zanr'ak.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_TODO_00<tab>Fouiller les <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E90C00302 /var> à l'ouest du camp de Zahar'ak pour reprendre les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E89140302 /var>

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_TODO_01<tab>Obtain a hunter's spear from an Amalj'aa brigand.
TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_TODO_02<tab>Obtain a stalker's bow from an Amalj'aa scavenger.
TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_TODO_03<tab>Deliver the weapons to Fibubb Gah.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_TODO_03<tab>Rapporter les accessoires miqo'tes à Fibubb Gah

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_001<tab>The Brotherhood of Ash strives to return our people to the selfsame glory our ancestors once knew. The fallen Amalj'aa, however, grind our honor into the dust with every misguided and ignoble step they take.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_001<tab>De fiers guerriers perpétuant l'esprit de la tradition amalj'aa, nous membres de la Ligue sommes. Hélas<var 1D /var>! Cette tradition, les Amalj'aa de Zahar'ak foulent aux pieds.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_002<tab>They swagger about like spoiled children, carrying weapons stripped from Miqo'te captives as if they were hard-won trophies of war...when in fact they are naught but garish reminders of craven ambushes and common pillaging.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_002<tab>L'équipement de chasse des Miqo'tes, ils ont dérobé. Se pavaner avec leur butin, ces sots osent ensuite. Digne des plus misérables des voleurs, ce com<var 16 /var>por<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment est.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_003<tab>It is said that the arms of the U tribe are passed down from one generation to the next─that these weapons are revered as highly as the teachings of their ancestors. Though we of the Brotherhood follow a different path, it is anathema to us that the honor of the Miqo'te should be so spat upon.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_003<tab>Transmis de génération en génération, les outils de chasse miqo'tes sont, à ce qu'on raconte. Nos amis, les Miqo'tes ne sont pas. Mais un com<var 16 /var>por<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment digne des Amalj'aa, humilier sans raison autrui n'est pas. Tolérer les vilenies de nos frères de race, nous ne saurions.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_004<tab>These Amalj'aa brigands and scavengers have not earned the right to their spoils. Search their camps, and reclaim all there is to be found. And when you have picked their caches clean, recover the rest from their bloody corpses.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_004<tab>Des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2056C0302 /var>, les coupables sont. Caché quelque part dans le camp, le fruit de leur larcin est sans doute. Fouiller l'endroit mi<var 16 /var>nu<var 16 /var>tieu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, tu devras. Le reprendre par la force il faudra, si dans les coffres tu ne le trouves pas.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_011<tab>Your enemies this day are the brigands and scavengers of the fallen Amalj'aa. Slay these swaggering fools for their affronts, and recover the ancestral weapons of the Miqo'te!
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_011<tab>Des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2056C0302 /var> et leurs acolytes, les coupables sont. Les armes des Miqo'tes, tu devras reprendre, par la force s'il le faut. L'affront fait à l'honneur des félins, tu devras laver au nom des guerriers amalj'aa.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_021<tab>Have you returned with the arms of the U tribe?
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_021<tab>Les objets volés aux félins, as-tu trouvé<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_022<tab>Yes, the weapons of the Miqo'te are distinct from any the Amalj'aa would craft. I will return these treasures to their Forgotten Springs heirs, and salvage some measure of honor for my people.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_022<tab>Les instruments de chasse des Miqo'tes, ce sont bien. Redevables des félins, nous ne sommes pas. Mais le respect des guerriers, nous leur devons. La moindre des choses, rapporter leurs outils à l'Oasis serait.

source: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_023<tab>Honored ally, once more you show a true warrior's spirit. Words are as wind, but your deeds mark your path into greatness.
target: TEXT_BANAMA109_01230_FIBUBBGAH_000_023<tab>Du beau travail, tu as accompli. Que la grandeur d'âme des guerriers t'animait, je ne doutais pas. Jusqu'au bout, leurs missions les véritables braves mènent.
